data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS TO INCLUDE $10,000 CREDIT TOWARD BUYERS CLOSING COST!  Discover the untapped potential of this vintage gem in Sun Valley. Nestled on a sprawling 1/3-acre lot, this 1979 converted manufactured home with 1560 sqft offers a canvas for your imagination and creativity. While the home may need a bit of TLC, envision the possibilities as you embark on transforming it into a truly charming and personalized haven. This property is priced to reflect its current condition, offering a fantastic opportunity for those with a vision for improvement. With some effort, this home has the potential to become a show-stopping residence in a desirable location. Make this home uniquely yours by investing the time and effort to bring out its full potential. Unleash your creativity and turn this diamond in the rough into a sparkling gem! The generous outdoor space beckons for landscaping and outdoor living enhancements. Picture a lush garden, a cozy patio, or even a potential space for entertaining friends and family.  Newer swamp cooler, furnace and water heater.
